Title: AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF BATOBATO, MUNICIPALITY OF CUYO, PROVINCE OF PALAWAN, TO THAT OF LOS ANGELES.
Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 575, June 08, 1940 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF BATOBATO, MUNICIPALITY OF CUYO, PROVINCE OF PALAWAN, TO THAT OF LOS ANGELES.
Be it enacted by the National Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The name of Barrio Batobato, Municipality of Cuyo, Province of Palawan, is changed to that of Los Angeles.ℒαwρhi৷
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Enacted, without Executive approval, June 8, 1940.
